{"tid":532991,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"如果自己去大坂 係咪唔應該去環球影城？","createTime":"2018-01-18T11:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T01:50:49.000Z","uid":75339,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1b5620b202c12f92860f9bc586cd1fca038278","tid":532991,"uid":75339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"我第一次自己去 大坂都係第一次去<br />\n雖然我唔係對機動遊戲好大興趣 但都想睇下入面係點既樣 個氣氛係點<br />\n但係自己一個去又好似好悶咁 而且大坂我都應該極大機會同屋企人去多次<br />\n咁我今次自己去 到底去唔去影城好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢張飛好似都幾貴下 我只去六日五夜 又想遊埋京都 奈良 如果去影城 應該就要冇左一日<br />\n大家成日去自由行既 可唔可以俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4efe8711f8774078b4f88f12ac3471bab4ee6f2","tid":532991,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95bb57fa612a9988b150021a5ece07b43f27ed72","tid":532991,"uid":75339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:04:18.000Z","msg":"發現自己錯字 大阪先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3344a418139cf30e37bf5cebbf12ff7bd19cba","tid":532991,"uid":35388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:05:25.000Z","msg":"無fd 有咩好玩"},{"pid":"a38957d9212bac381dbaefd5507a8587cf298511","tid":532991,"uid":8850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:07:06.000Z","msg":"單機當然係睇景啦"},{"pid":"84fe14bd5535b6b885a33311a93483281e5952f5","tid":532991,"uid":42510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"如果你屋企人鐘意玩機動遊戲就等埋屋企人先去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己一個去遊樂場會有啲悶，排隊會唔知做乜尻好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 入面係幾好玩氣氛都好好，去過三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e637b0e6317d35f71b2f6971cd53fbc57cf53bb6","tid":532991,"uid":138313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b1b5620b202c12f92860f9bc586cd1fca038278","tid":532991,"uid":75339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"我第一次自己去 大坂都係第一次去<br />\n雖然我唔係對機動遊戲好大興趣 但都想睇下入面係點既樣 個氣氛係點<br />\n但係自己一個去又好似好悶咁 而且大坂我都應該極大機會同屋企人去多次<br />\n咁我今次自己去 到底去唔去影城好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢張飛好似都幾貴下 我只去六日五夜 又想遊埋京都 奈良 如果去影城 應該就要冇左一日<br />\n大家成日去自由行既 可唔可以俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T12:02:52.000Z","msg":"睇你想玩機動定睇下風景咁，玩機動一個人排隊好悶，淨係去下哈利波特睇下巡遊個啲就一個人都得，另外如果係去京奈，不妨將去環球影城押後，環球其實唔急去"},{"pid":"e503a9ab4fdd6302cbf279dc5cb1eb30d7fc87cf","tid":532991,"uid":138313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4efe8711f8774078b4f88f12ac3471bab4ee6f2","tid":532991,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T12:12:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ja.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/大阪\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fja.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA&d=9dMuYyAIBpaWJZUsR8q3Yozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5c3ffc61\" target=\"_blank\">https://ja.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/大阪</a><br />\n大坂其實係大阪古字黎，依家係一啲舊書或者舊地圖都可以見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92a7eebe14c93ba961b27455aab12702dce6cf0","tid":532991,"uid":34929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"之前先自己去完東京迪士尼 好撚正<br />\n一個人可以單刷哂所有景點<br />\n睇下你頂唔頂得順一個人排隊"},{"pid":"049ef3b57fcc3756185dc0cd2993f9701e3165fd","tid":532991,"uid":22932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"環球影城有單人隊排<br />\n自己一個去幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時自己一個去 四圍行下<br />\n望下日本妹幾好feel"},{"pid":"740e6f2ce3d6719a5ffa5eb7bd17be13d7f5ec2f","tid":532991,"uid":4234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"自己一個好快㗎排隊，自己去一次先好<br />\n同屋企人未必肯個個game都陪你排"},{"pid":"6336cddca4b68da86019aaa00db79b944df0db6a","tid":532991,"uid":129145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T13:08:23.000Z","msg":"前幾日自己一個去完 覺得好好玩 <br />\nD staff 好熱情 唔覺得悶<br />\n有d隊一個人排仲可以快d到添"},{"pid":"3fdbfea29653aa332639ce3977f947414c0a7b6c","tid":532991,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6336cddca4b68da86019aaa00db79b944df0db6a","tid":532991,"uid":129145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T13:08:23.000Z","msg":"前幾日自己一個去完 覺得好好玩 <br />\nD staff 好熱情 唔覺得悶<br />\n有d隊一個人排仲可以快d到添"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T19:05:46.000Z","msg":"屌我都係前幾日一個人去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰日都算幾小人排得最耐都係一粒鐘 <br />\n哈利波特嗰啲排半粒鐘有得玩<br />\n蜘蛛俠牌單人排咗兩個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兩個熱門我都各自玩左兩次<br />\n雖然一個人有啲毒<br />\n但都冇人會記得你㗎啦<br />\n咁難得去到咪玩吓囉<br />\n同埋啲staff真係幾好人<br />\n我帶住嗰啲頭飾經過會話kawaii呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4808dac4abd0cd068697755e33ccd0f1431da0","tid":532991,"uid":13193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fdbfea29653aa332639ce3977f947414c0a7b6c","tid":532991,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6336cddca4b68da86019aaa00db79b944df0db6a","tid":532991,"uid":129145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T13:08:23.000Z","msg":"前幾日自己一個去完 覺得好好玩 <br />\nD staff 好熱情 唔覺得悶<br />\n有d隊一個人排仲可以快d到添"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T19:05:46.000Z","msg":"屌我都係前幾日一個人去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰日都算幾小人排得最耐都係一粒鐘 <br />\n哈利波特嗰啲排半粒鐘有得玩<br />\n蜘蛛俠牌單人排咗兩個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兩個熱門我都各自玩左兩次<br />\n雖然一個人有啲毒<br />\n但都冇人會記得你㗎啦<br />\n咁難得去到咪玩吓囉<br />\n同埋啲staff真係幾好人<br />\n我帶住嗰啲頭飾經過會話kawaii呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"唔算少人啦，我1月8號去<br />\n哈利波特可以玩完再玩，排都唔使排<br />\n玩到想嘔<br />\n排最耐係minion 十分鐘<br />\n嗰日係日本公眾假期不過落微雨 買咗fast pass都唔使用 哂錢"}]}